+## FILE CREATION GOVERNANCE POLICY
+
+### Overview
+
+To prevent documentation sprawl and maintain a clean repository structure, all agents must follow strict file creation rules.
+
+### Single Collaboration Surface
+
+**COCKPIT/WORKSPACE/TEAM_LOG.md** is the ONLY place for:
+- Brainstorming and coordination
+- Review notes and commentary
+- Questions and decisions
+- Progress updates outside PRs
+- Gap lists and risk discussions
+
+### Permitted File Creation
+
+Agents MAY create new files ONLY if:
+
+1. **PR-Bound Artifacts**:
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/PLAN/PLAN-*.md`
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/EXECUTION/EXEC-*.md`
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/VERIFICATION/VER-*.md`
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/TRAE_REVIEW/TRAE-*.yml`
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/DAILY_BRIEF/BRIEF-*.md`
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/APPROVALS_QUEUE/APPROVALS-*.md`
+   - `COCKPIT/artifacts/ROLLBACK/ROLLBACK-*.md`
+
+2. **Canonical Documentation** (requires founder approval):
+   - `FOUNDATION/*` (company constitution)
+   - `PRODUCT/*` (product canon)
+   - `GOVERNANCE/*` (governance rules)
+
+3. **Code and Tests** (normal development):
+   - `APP/**` (application code)
+   - `tests/**` (test files)
+   - `.github/workflows/**` (CI/CD)
+
+### Prohibited File Creation
+
+Agents MUST NOT create:
+- ❌ Random markdown files in `COCKPIT/`
+- ❌ Ad-hoc "notes" or "scratch" files
+- ❌ Duplicate coordination documents
+- ❌ "DISCUSSION-*.md" or similar files
+- ❌ Files outside approved directory structure
+
+### Enforcement
+
+**Before creating any new file**, agents must verify:
+1. Is this a PR-bound artifact? → Use `COCKPIT/artifacts/[TYPE]/`
+2. Is this coordination/discussion? → Append to `TEAM_LOG.md`
+3. Is this canonical documentation? → Requires founder approval
+4. Is this code/tests? → Use `APP/` or `tests/`
+5. Otherwise → DO NOT CREATE
+
+**Violation Handling**:
+- PRs creating files outside approved areas will be flagged by governance validator
+- Advisory warning (not blocking) to encourage compliance
+
+
